\c 7
\nb
\v 1 Kwathi uSolomoni eseqedile ukukhuleka\x + 1 Kho. 8.54.\x*, umlilo wehla uvela emazulwini, wadla umnikelo wokutshiswa lemihlatshelo\x + 1 Lan. 21.26. Levi 9.24.\x*, lenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yagcwalisa indlu\x + 5.13. 1 Kho. 8.10,11.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo abapristi babengelakho ukungena endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yayigcwalise indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 5.14.\x*.
\v 3 Lapho bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli bebona ukwehla komlilo lenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* phezu kwendlu, bakhothama ngobuso babo emhlabathini endaweni egandelweyo, bakhonza bedumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi ilungile, ukuthi umusa wayo \add umi\add* phakade\x + 7.6. 5.13.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Inkosi labo bonke abantu banikela-ke imihlatshelo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 5 Inkosi uSolomoni yasinikela imihlatshelo yezinkabi ezizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili, lezimvu ezizinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili. Ngokunjalo inkosi labo bonke abantu bayehlukanisa indlu kaNkulunkulu.
\v 6 Abapristi basebesima ezikhundleni zabo; lamaLevi elezinto zokuhlabelela zikaJehova inkosi uDavida ayezenzele ukudumisa uJehova, ngoba umusa wakhe \add umi\add* phakade, lapho uDavida edumisa ngenkonzo yabo; labapristi bakhalisa impondo phambi kwabo, loIsrayeli wonke wema.
\v 7 USolomoni wasengcwelisa iphakathi leguma elaliphambi kwendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba wenza lapho iminikelo yokutshiswa lamahwahwa eminikelo yokuthula, ngoba ilathi lethusi uSolomoni ayelenzile lalingenele umnikelo wokutshiswa, lomnikelo wokudla, lamahwahwa.
\p
\v 8 Langalesosikhathi uSolomoni wenza umkhosi okwensuku eziyisikhombisa, loIsrayeli wonke kanye laye, ibandla elikhulu kakhulu, kusukela ekungeneni kweHamathi kusiya esifuleni seGibhithe.
\v 9 Langosuku lwesificaminwembili benza umhlangano onzulu, ngoba benza ukwehlukaniswa kwelathi okwensuku eziyisikhombisa, lomkhosi okwensuku eziyisikhombisa.
\v 10 Ngosuku lwamatshumi amabili lantathu lwenyanga yesikhombisa waseyekela abantu bahamba baya emathenteni abo, bethokoza bejabula enhliziyweni ngokuhle iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayikwenzele uDavida loSolomoni loIsrayeli abantu bayo.
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* izibonakalisa kuSolomoni
\p
\v 11 Ngokunjalo uSolomoni waqeda indlu kaJehova lendlu yenkosi; lakho konke okwakuvela enhliziyweni kaSolomoni ukukwenza endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* lendlini yakhe wakuphumelelisa\x + 1 Kho. 9.1-9.\x*.
\p
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakala kuSolomoni ebusuku yathi kuye: Ngizwile umkhuleko wakho, sengizikhethele lindawo ukuba yindlu yomhlatshelo\x + 7.16. Dute. 12.5.\x*.
\v 13 Uba ngivala amazulu ukuze kungabi lazulu\x + 6.26,28.\x*, kumbe uba ngilaya intethe ukuqeda ilizwe, kumbe uba ngithumela umatshayabhuqe wesifo phakathi kwabantu bami\x + Nani 13.33.\x*,
\v 14 uba abantu bami ibizo lami elibizwa phezu kwabo bezithoba, bakhuleke badinge ubuso bami, baphenduke ezindleleni zabo ezimbi\x + 12.7.\x*, mina-ke ngizakuzwa ngisemazulwini, ngithethelele isono sabo, ngelaphe ilizwe labo\x + 6.27,30.\x*.
\v 15 Khathesi amehlo ami azavuleka, lendlebe zami zilalele umkhuleko walindawo\x + 6.40.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba sengiyikhethile ngayingcwelisa lindlu ukuze ibizo lami libe khona kuze kube nininini; lamehlo ami lenhliziyo yami kuzakuba lapho zonke izinsuku\x + 7.12. 6.6.\x*.
\v 17 Wena-ke, uba uhamba phambi kwami njengokuhamba kukaDavida uyihlo, wenze njengakho konke engikulaye khona, ugcine izimiso zami lezahlulelo zami,
\v 18 ngizaqinisa-ke isihlalo sobukhosi sombuso wakho, njengokwenza kwami \add isivumelwano\add* loDavida uyihlo ngisithi: Kakuyikusweleka\f + \fk kakuyikusweleka: \fl Heb. \fq kakuyikuqunywa.\f* muntu kuwe obusa koIsrayeli.
\v 19 Kodwa uba libuyela emuva lina, litshiya izimiso zami lemilayo yami engikubeke phambi kwenu, lihambe likhonze abanye onkulunkulu libakhothamele\x + Levi 26.14. Dute. 28.15.\x*,
\v 20 ngizabasiphuna-ke elizweni engibanike lona, lalindlu engiyingcwelisele ibizo lami ngizayilahla isuke phambi kwami, ngiyenze ibe yisiga lento yokuhozwa phakathi kwezizwe zonke\x + Dute. 29.28.\x*.
\v 21 Lalindlu ephakemeyo izakuba yisimangaliso kulowo lalowo odlula kuyo, aze athi: IN\nd kosi\nd* ikwenzeleni okunje kulelilizwe lakulindlu?
\v 22 Bazakuthi-ke: Kungoba beyidelile iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyise eyabakhupha elizweni leGibhithe, babambelela kwabanye onkulunkulu, babakhonza babasebenzela; ngenxa yalokho ibehlisele bonke lobububi.